<p>If you have any suggestions or questions, I would love to hear them. 
Please feel free to e-mail me at shane.colbert@gmail.com.
If you have any suggestions, or wish to help out, the project is on github.
</p><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="https://github.com/shanecolb/sphinx-ue4">https://github.com/shanecolb/sphinx-ue4</a>
</p>
